Rating: 4
Try this. Get rid of the egg whites and whip up 1/2 liter cream. This is sooo much better. And to prevent it being too "soupy", put it in the freezer. You can enjoy it as ice cream or defrost it to your preferred texture. AND it prevents the ladyfingers from getting too soggy.

